Christian Nold and The Bijlmer Euro

Webcast via http://blip.tv/play/AYGN2g6Y2m4


=Description=

"In this interview of Christian Nold by Stowe Boyd, an artist, designer and educator working to develop new participatory models for communal representation, discusses his project in the Bijlmer area in South East Amsterdam, where he aimed to develop a prototype system for an alternative local currency that could support local development and work in conjunction with the Euro."
(http://www.stoweboyd.com/message/2009/06/the-future-of-money-christian-nold.html)


